<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 08:11:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>泰国距离成为第一个批准同性婚姻的东南亚国家又近了一步</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/thailand-becomes-first-southeast-asian-country-to-approve-same-sex-marriage/articleshow/111077499.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111077499.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 07:34:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/thailand-becomes-first-southeast-asian-country-to-approve-same-sex-marriage/articleshow/111077499.cms</guid></item><item><title>从冻结到走神：白宫回应指控拜登精神衰退的视频</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/freezing-to-wandering-off-white-house-responds-to-videos-alleging-bidens-mental-decline/articleshow/111073979.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111073979.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 04:57:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/freezing-to-wandering-off-white-house-responds-to-videos-alleging-bidens-mental-decline/articleshow/111073979.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦男子因非法侵入而砍断骆驼腿并发布视频</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistani-men-cut-camels-leg-for-trespassing-post-video/articleshow/111074338.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111074338.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦的一名男子和他的五名仆人在骆驼进入他的田地作为饲料后砍断了它的腿。这起事件上周末发生在信德省桑加尔区的 Mund Jamrao 村。随后，他在网上分享了一段视频，展示了骆驼被肢解的腿，该视频在社交媒体上引起了广泛关注。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 05:18:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistani-men-cut-camels-leg-for-trespassing-post-video/articleshow/111074338.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国：佐治亚州房屋火灾造成6人死亡、5人受伤，其中包括3名儿童</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-6-people-including-3-children-killed-5-injured-in-georgia-house-fire/articleshow/111073450.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111073450.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 04:26:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-6-people-including-3-children-killed-5-injured-in-georgia-house-fire/articleshow/111073450.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登新政策为美国公民配偶提供驱逐保护和工作许可</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bidens-new-policy-to-offer-deportation-protection-work-permits-for-spouses-of-us-citizens/articleshow/111072930.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111072930.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统拜登的新政策将为美国公民的配偶提供“就地假释”计划，提供工作许可和驱逐保护。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 03:43:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bidens-new-policy-to-offer-deportation-protection-work-permits-for-spouses-of-us-citizens/articleshow/111072930.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾密切关注中国潜艇在台湾海峡浮出水面</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-keeping-watch-after-chinese-submarine-surfaces-in-taiwan-strait/articleshow/111071978.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111071978.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;台湾国防部长谈到了对在台湾海峡附近发现的中国核潜艇的担忧，强调台湾的监视能力，但没有透露具体细节。由于中国继续在该地区进行军事活动，包括频繁的飞行和海军存在，紧张局势持续存在。台湾仍然对旨在改变现状的灰色地带策略保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 02:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-keeping-watch-after-chinese-submarine-surfaces-in-taiwan-strait/articleshow/111071978.cms</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥即将上任的总统表示，调查显示支持有争议的司法改革</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mexicos-incoming-president-says-surveys-show-support-for-controversial-judicial-reforms/articleshow/111071834.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111071834.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;即将上任的墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆公布的调查显示，大多数人支持有争议的司法改革。批评者认为，这些调查，就像她的导师洛佩兹·奥夫拉多尔所使用的那样，更多的是作为公关策略。这些调查由独立民意调查机构进行，表明公众强烈希望有一个独立机构来监督司法腐败。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 02:42:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mexicos-incoming-president-says-surveys-show-support-for-controversial-judicial-reforms/articleshow/111071834.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国总理访澳重点关注关键矿产和清洁能源</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-premier-focuses-on-critical-minerals-and-clean-energy-during-australian-visit/articleshow/111071773.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111071773.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国总理李强在珀斯结束了澳大利亚之行，强调了中国在关键矿产和清洁能源方面的投资。由于澳大利亚担心中国对该行业的影响力，他参观了 Fortescue 的清洁能源设施和一家锂加工厂。中国官员干扰澳大利亚记者也引发了紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 02:38:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-premier-focuses-on-critical-minerals-and-clean-energy-during-australian-visit/articleshow/111071773.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜士兵越境后韩国鸣枪示警</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korean-fires-warning-shots-after-north-korean-soldiers-cross-border/articleshow/111071797.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111071797.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 02:43:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korean-fires-warning-shots-after-north-korean-soldiers-cross-border/articleshow/111071797.cms</guid></item><item><title>疑似地中海移民事故 51人疏散 10多人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/51-evacuated-over-10-dead-in-suspected-mediterranean-migration-accident/articleshow/111070574.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111070574.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; RESQSHIP 在 X 上的一篇帖子中表示，他们的船员正在“照顾”从船上撤离的 51 人。 “对于10人来说，救援来得太晚了。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 00:17:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/51-evacuated-over-10-dead-in-suspected-mediterranean-migration-accident/articleshow/111070574.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国指责菲律宾补给船在南海撞击中国船只</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-accuses-philippine-supply-ship-of-hitting-chinese-vessel-in-south-china-sea/articleshow/111069385.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111069385.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国和菲律宾因南海碰撞事件发生冲突，紧张局势升级。美国与日本、加拿大和菲律宾在后者专属经济区完成了联合海军演习。对危险演习和入侵的指控加剧了该地区长期存在的争端。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:57:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-accuses-philippine-supply-ship-of-hitting-chinese-vessel-in-south-china-sea/articleshow/111069385.cms</guid></item><item><title>意大利附近两艘沉船造成 11 名移民死亡、64 人失踪；巴基斯坦，孟加拉国国民在船上</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/11-migrants-dead-64-missing-in-two-shipwrecks-off-italy-pak-bangladesh-natls-on-board/articleshow/111069124.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111069124.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;意大利南部海域发生悲惨事件，造成 11 名移民死亡、64 人失踪。德国慈善机构 RESQSHIP 从一艘下沉的木船上救出了 51 人，其中包括来自叙利亚、埃及、巴基斯坦、孟加拉国、伊朗和伊拉克的幸存者。幸存者被移交给意大利海岸警卫队。联合国机构确认了移民的国籍，并找到了一名妇女的尸体。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:51:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/11-migrants-dead-64-missing-in-two-shipwrecks-off-italy-pak-bangladesh-natls-on-board/articleshow/111069124.cms</guid></item><item><title>希腊海岸警卫队是否将移民扔入海中？政府否认新报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/did-greece-coast-guard-throw-migrants-into-sea-government-denies-new-report/articleshow/111068542.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111068542.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;希腊否认有关虐待移民的报道。否认非法阻止寻求庇护者。 BBC 援引爱琴海岛屿附近发生的 43 起移民溺水事件。喀麦隆男子声称蒙面男子参与了萨摩斯岛事件。叙利亚男子讲述了在罗德岛附近被遗弃在救生筏中的幸存者的故事。土耳其海岸警卫队未提及。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:38:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/did-greece-coast-guard-throw-migrants-into-sea-government-denies-new-report/articleshow/111068542.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京扩大国防部清洗，将工作交给亲戚</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-extends-defence-ministry-purge-hands-job-to-a-relative/articleshow/111067816.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067816.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京解雇了四名国防部副部长，任命安娜·齐维列娃负责军事支持，并重点关注预算效率。此次重组旨在打击国防部内最近发生的丑闻中的腐败行为。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-extends-defence-ministry-purge-hands-job-to-a-relative/articleshow/111067816.cms</guid></item><item><title>PIO女子在美国遭枪击身亡，另一人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pio-woman-killed-another-injured-after-being-shot-at-in-us/articleshow/111067972.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067972.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新泽西州发生一起悲惨枪击事件，29岁的印度裔妇女贾斯维尔·考尔被杀，她20岁的表弟受重伤。 19 岁的犯罪嫌疑人高拉夫·吉尔 (Gaurav Gill) 已被拘留，面临一级谋杀等指控。枪击事件的动机尚不清楚，当局呼吁提供与此案相关的信息。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:22:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pio-woman-killed-another-injured-after-being-shot-at-in-us/articleshow/111067972.cms</guid></item><item><title>保存奇迹：在美国第一任总统乔治·华盛顿的官邸发现了拥有 250 年历史的樱桃</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/preservation-marvel-250-year-old-cherries-discovered-at-first-us-president-george-washingtons-mansion/articleshow/111067712.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067712.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最近在乔治·华盛顿的弗农山庄庄园进行的考古发现揭示了瓶中保存完好的樱桃和浆果，挑战了他砍倒樱桃树的神话。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/preservation-marvel-250-year-old-cherries-discovered-at-first-us-president-george-washingtons-mansion/articleshow/111067712.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯普京将访问越南，引发美国对河内的斥责</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russias-putin-to-visit-vietnam-sparking-us-rebuke-of-hanoi/articleshow/111067708.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067708.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京访问河内强调越南对俄罗斯的效忠，遭到美国的严厉谴责。这次访问旨在展示越南平衡的外交政策，接待了乔·拜登和习近平等重要领导人。预计将就贸易、投资、武器、能源和支付系统进行讨论。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:14:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russias-putin-to-visit-vietnam-sparking-us-rebuke-of-hanoi/articleshow/111067708.cms</guid></item><item><title>北约主席称各国正在谈判让核武器处于待命状态</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nato-chief-says-nations-in-talks-to-put-n-weapons-on-standby/articleshow/111067651.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067651.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;北约正在考虑部署更多核武器，以应对来自俄罗斯和中国日益增加的威胁。北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格强调了透明度在传达北约核能力立场方面的重要性。尽管目标是建立一个没有核武器的世界，但只要其他国家拥有核武器，北约仍然致力于维持核武器。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:07:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nato-chief-says-nations-in-talks-to-put-n-weapons-on-standby/articleshow/111067651.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国外科医生呼吁在社交媒体平台上贴上警告标签</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-surgeon-gen-calls-for-warning-labels-on-social-media-platforms/articleshow/111067605.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067605.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国卫生局局长维韦克·穆尔蒂（Vivek Murthy）主张在社交媒体平台上贴上警告标签，提醒家长青少年面临的潜在心理健康风险。穆蒂博士强调需要国会批准，并将社交媒体对年轻人的影响与重大公共卫生风险进行比较。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:01:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-surgeon-gen-calls-for-warning-labels-on-social-media-platforms/articleshow/111067605.cms</guid></item><item><title>瑞士检察官：印度人在宠物狗上花的钱比他们支付的帮助还要多</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/hindujas-spent-more-on-pet-dog-than-they-paid-a-help-swiss-prosecutor/articleshow/111067559.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067559.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;瑞士检察官透露，辛杜贾家族在日内瓦湖别墅的宠物狗上的花费比在仆人上的花费还要多。据称，仆人在长时间工作期间支付 7 瑞士法郎的费用，并且自由受到限制。家庭纠纷索赔，理由是对员工的尊重。 Ajay Hinduja 称招聘由印度 Hinduja 集团管理，而法庭则仔细权衡证据。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:55:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/hindujas-spent-more-on-pet-dog-than-they-paid-a-help-swiss-prosecutor/articleshow/111067559.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>